oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Webb Pierce, Koko the clown, and Carl Smith at the Nichols Park
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Pierce, Webb, 1921-1991; Smith, Carl, 1927-2010; Lance, Lynda K.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing the Grand Ole Opry stars Webb Pierce, Koko the Clown, Carl Smith, Jack Barlow, Lynda K. Lance. and the Homesteaders at Nichols Park on July 4. Poster features metal photoplates of Webb Pierce, Koko, Carl Smith, and Lynda Lance.
